agilermi.utility.io

Interface RandomAccessService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable, Remote

    public interface RandomAccessService
extends java.io.Closeable, Remote
    Remote interface used to access a random access file remotely. The server should use the RafToRas or another proper implementation of this interface to provide access to a random access file or to a similar data storage.
    Author:
    Salvatore Giampa'
